# selectableMapFeatures

**Interface Property**

An array of map features that someone can select from the map.

## Declaration

```swift
selectableMapFeatures?: MapFeatureType[];
```

## Discussion

The map displays this array of the selectable map features from the types available in [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/MapFeatureType].
